CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 26, 2008

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1311. Doe v. Massillon City School Dist.

Stark App. No. 2006CA00227, 2007-0hio-2801. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Stark County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to seal the second supplement,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
